OL,5, One of the so-called "godfathers" of   
OL,6, Artificial Intelligence (AI) has said  
OL,7, he would have prioritised safety over  
OL,8, usefulness had he realised the pace at 
OL,9, which it would evolve.                 
OL,11,FProf Yoshua Bengio told the BBC he felt
OL,12,F"lost" over his life's work.           
OL,14,FThe computer scientist's comments come 
OL,15,Fafter experts in AI said it could lead 
OL,16,Fto the extinction of humanity.         
OL,18,FProf Bengio, who has joined calls for  
OL,19,FAI regulation, said he did not think   
OL,20,Fmilitaries should be granted AI powers.
